<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Guadalajara Oculta</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@700&family=Spectral:ital@1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Fondo animado de niebla */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: url('https://i.imgur.com/1ZQZ1Zy.png') repeat;
      animation: fog 60s linear infinite;
      color: #dcdcdc;
      font-family: 'Spectral', serif;
    }

    @keyframes fog {
      0% { background-position: 0 0; }
      100% { background-position: 1000px 0; }
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #b30059;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px #660033;
    }

    header p {
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: #aaa;
      animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in;
    }

    section {
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.85);
      margin: 2rem auto;
      max-width: 800px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px #330019;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    section:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    section h2 {
      font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
      color: #e60073;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    section p {
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
    }

    iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px #660033;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .contact-button {
      display: block;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background-color: #660033;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #99004d;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact-button:hover {
      background-color: #99004d;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      background-color: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.9);
      color: #666;
    }

    .social-icons img {
      width: 40px;
      margin: 0 10px;
      filter: grayscale(100%) brightness(0.8);
      transition: filter 0.3s ease;
    }

    .social-icons img:hover {
      filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(1.2);
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Guadalajara Oculta</h1>
    <p>Explora los secretos que susurran entre sombras</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Mazamitla</h2>
    <p>Donde la niebla abraza los pinos y los susurros se esconden entre cabañas.</p>
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID_1" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Chapala</h2>
    <p>El lago refleja más que agua… refleja historias que no se han contado.</p>
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID_2" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tequila</h2>
    <p>Entre agaves y barricas, se destilan leyendas que arden en la garganta.</p>
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID_3" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Guadalajara</h2>
    <p>Bajo sus cúpulas y callejones, la ciudad murmura secretos de siglos pasados.</p>
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID_4" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </section>

  <a class="contact-button" href="https://wa.me/52XXXXXXXXXX" target="_blank">Reserva tu experiencia</a>

  <footer>
    <div class="social-icons">
      <a href="https://instagram.com"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/1xXfZlK.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
      <a href="https://tiktok.com"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/2ZcYw7v.png" alt="TikTok"></a>
      <a href="https://youtube.com"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/3VZz5gJ.png" alt="YouTube"></a>
    </div>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Guadalajara Oculta</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

